{{Main|Japanese creation myth}}
[[File:Kobayashi Izanami and Izanagi.jpg|thumb|200px|[[Izanagi]] (right) and [[Izanami]] (left) consolidating the earth with the spear Ama-no-Nuboko. Painting by Eitaku Kobayashi ([[Meiji (era)|Meiji period]])]]

